title: Episode 230: Movies, Movies, Movies! W/Josh Lindsay
description: Podcast co-host Skye Jethani and Josh Lindsay are launching a new podcast about movies, so with Skye off in India, Phil and Christian sit down with Josh to talk movies and the new podcast!
